WEBVTT

00:00.063 --> 00:02.828
All right, quickly finish
shutting up, everybody.

00:03.508 --> 00:05.350
I have an awesome new Miles mission.

00:05.810 --> 00:07.821
We're gonna make him a deadbeat dad.

00:08.412 --> 00:10.349
Hold up, wouldn't he
have to be a dad first?

00:10.350 --> 00:12.134
Dan, you're great at this class.

00:12.159 --> 00:13.126
I am?

00:13.128 --> 00:14.625
So I was looking for dirt on Miles,

00:14.626 --> 00:16.126
and I found an old
photograph of us together

00:16.128 --> 00:18.564
with this girl, Theresa,
that he had a fling with.

00:18.589 --> 00:22.057
Now, if he had gotten her
pregnant without realizing it,

00:22.059 --> 00:24.193
then their child would now be,

00:24.195 --> 00:26.862
oh, about your age.

00:30.000 --> 00:31.259
What're you do... Anthony?

00:32.320 --> 00:33.683
Pass the photo around.

00:34.472 --> 00:35.771
Well, look at it first.

00:35.773 --> 00:37.172
Never mind... Anyway...

00:37.174 --> 00:39.484
One of you is gonna
bring this photo to Miles

00:39.484 --> 00:40.883
and say that that's your mom,

00:40.885 --> 00:42.736
and that you're his kid that he abandoned.

00:43.137 --> 00:45.070
Voila. Deadbeat dad.

00:45.072 --> 00:47.472
And the best part is,
you're gonna tell him this

00:47.474 --> 00:51.209
right before he walks on stage
in Detroit for a TED Talk.

00:51.211 --> 00:53.078
It's gonna totally mess with his head.

00:53.080 --> 00:55.256
It's gonna ruin his presentation.

00:55.816 --> 00:57.382
The only question that remains is,

00:57.382 --> 01:00.116
Which one of you can most convincingly

01:00.118 --> 01:02.516
play the role of Miles' kid?

01:03.121 --> 01:04.500
Let me see what you guys got.

01:06.005 --> 01:08.305
I've missed you ever since I was a...

01:08.307 --> 01:09.774
Too slow. Too slow.

01:09.776 --> 01:12.386
Okay, Heather. You're
face to face with Miles.

01:12.819 --> 01:14.145
What're you gonna do?

01:14.921 --> 01:16.854
Well, hey there, big daddy.

01:16.856 --> 01:18.876
Nope. Mm-mm, wrong tone.

01:19.259 --> 01:22.093
Am I the only one who feels
like making Miles think

01:22.095 --> 01:24.562
he has a kid might be
going a little too far?

01:24.564 --> 01:25.897
Miles is lame.

01:25.899 --> 01:27.832
He deserves everything
that's coming to him.

01:27.834 --> 01:30.268
He's peddling these fake philosophies

01:30.270 --> 01:33.489
to the ignorant masses and he knows better.

01:33.740 --> 01:35.339
Yes. Devin gets it.

01:35.341 --> 01:37.308
This is exactly what
I've been talking about.

01:37.310 --> 01:38.523
Okay, Devin. So...

01:39.211 --> 01:40.897
Tell me how you break the news to him.

01:41.414 --> 01:44.454
Miles, you're my dad, and you suck.

01:45.940 --> 01:48.908
There's our guy, right there.
The Prince of Darkness is back.

01:48.910 --> 01:50.776
I love it. I'm gonna need to confiscate

01:50.778 --> 01:52.123
that knife from you, though, bud.

01:52.123 --> 01:53.389
Uh, I think I've let
things get a little bit

01:53.390 --> 01:54.656
too loose around here.

01:54.658 --> 01:55.890
Go ahead and finish crossing the A

01:55.892 --> 01:57.458
on your anarchy thing, though.

